        "message":"There's not much else to tell at this point. We have looked around, but there's not much here other than the road and the forest. There's a couple of old women living in a shack just down the road, but they say they have seen nothing unusual. Of course, we intend to search more thoroughly, but there is no huge rush to do so unless another child goes missing. Our camp here is comfortable, with good food and beer available in the local town. If we figure out what is going on we might be sent on a mission to some horrible, dangerous, place [smirks]!",
        "replies":[
            {
                "text":"I'll do my best to solve it quickly, so that you can be on your way.",
                "nextPhraseID":"X"
